name: Laura Overbo
bio: While Laura is newer to improv comedy, she is no stranger improvising! With experience from TBD Comedy, she's a member who likes to work behind the scenes but still likes to be surrounded by laughter.

name: Chuck Kanoy
bio: Chuck has worked with TBD Comedy and Tornado Shelter Improv practicing improv comedy. He gets a real kick out of physical comedy and silent scenes. His favorite scene he's ever done took place in a gravel pit, but he'd never admit that to you.

name: Josh Fenner
bio: Josh has been an imp-roviser for many years having previously worked with TBD Comedy and hosting Tornado Shelter Improv. When asked how he discovered his talent for comedy, all Josh would say is "The devil made me do it!"

name: Matt Smith
bio: Matt has been a part of improv as the president of TBD at NDSU, a member of Tornado Shelter, and an educator of improv through Trollwood and coaching at south High School. Matt still has no idea what he’s doing. He walked into a room in the middle of a scene and just said “yes and”.
